f="http://www.engconf.org/staging/conferences/biotechnology/oligonucleotide-delivery/">Oct 7-11, 2012</a> (12AF) OLIGONUCLEOTIDE DELIVERY: BIOLOGY, ENGINEERING AND DEVELOPMENT</strong> (Hernstein, Austria)\r\n(L. Sepp-Lorenzino, Merck &amp; Co., Inc.; S. F. Dowdy, Univ of California San Diego School of Medicine; Michael Gait, MRC Laboratory of Molecular Biology, UK; Gilles Divita, CNRS, France)\r\n\r\n<strong><a title="Advanced Membrane Technology V" href="http://www.engconf.org/staging/conferences/chemical-engineering/advanced-membrane-technology-v/">Oct 14-19, 2012</a> (12AM) ADVANCED MEMBRANE TECHNOLOGY V</strong> (Singapore)\r\n(T. Fane, Nanyang Technological Univ.; R. Wang, Nanyang Technological Univ.)\r\n\r\n<strong>Conferences in 2013</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><a title="Fluidization XIV: From Fundamentals To Products" href="http://www.engconf.org/staging/conferences/chemical-engineering/fluidization-xiv-from-fundamentals-to-products/">May 25-30, 2013</a> (13AF) FLUIDIZATION XIV: FROM FUNDAMENTALS TO PRODUCTS </strong> (Noordwijkerhout, The Netherlands)\r\n(J.A.M. Kuipers and N.G. Deen, TU Eindhoven; R.F. Mudde and J.R. van Ommen, Delft Univ. of Technology)\r\n\r\n<strong><a title="Biochemical And Molecular Engineering XVIII" href="http://www.engconf.org/staging/conferences/biotechnology/biochemical-and-molecular-engineering-xviii/">June 16-20, 2013</a> (13AM) BIOCHEMICAL AND MOLECULAR ENGINEERING XVIII</strong> (Beijing, China)\r\n(Honorary Chairs: Daniel I.C. Wang, MIT; Pinkai Ouyang, Nanjing Chemical University; H. Zhao, Univ. of Illinois; D. Robinson, Merck)\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Chemical Engineering', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chemical-engineering', '', '', '2012-03-28 03:29:53', '2012-03-28 03:29:53', '', 11, 'http://www.engconf.org/staging/?page_id=389', 2, 'page', '', 0); 
