f California San Diego, CA, USA.\r\nRobert Schroter, Imperial College London, UK.\r\nYacov Shamash, Stony Brook University, NY, USA.\r\nSatya Sharma, Stony Brook University, NY, USA.\r\nSpencer Sherwin, Imperial College London, UK.\r\nMarvin Slepian, University of Arizona, AZ, USA.\r\nFotis Sotiropoulos, University of Minnesota, MN, USA.\r\nMaria Siebes, University of Amsterdam, The Netherlands.\r\nDavid Steinman, University of Toronto, Canada.\r\nUlrich Steinseifer, RWTH Aachen University, Germany.\r\nGábor Székely, Swiss Federal Institute of Technology (ETH), Switzerland.\r\nDalin Tang, Worcester Polytechnic Institute, MA, USA.\r\nJohn Tarbell, City College of the City University of New York, NY, USA.\r\nMerryn Tawhai, The University of Auckland, New Zealand.\r\nCharles Taylor, Stanford University, CA, USA.\r\nMarc Thiriet, Universite Pierre et Marie Curie (Paris VI), France.\r\nPascal Verdonck, Ghent University, Belgium.\r\nDavid Vorp, University of Pittsburgh, PA, USA.\r\nFrans van de Vosse, Eindhoven University of Technology, The Netherlands\r\nSheldon Weinbaum, City College of the City University of New York, NY, USA.\r\nDaniel Weihs, Technion, Israel.\r\nAjit Yoganathan, Georgia Institute of Technology, GA, USA.\r\nMair Zamir, The University of Western Ontario, Canada.\r\n\r\n<strong>Final Program</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.engconf.org/staging/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/12adfin.pdf">Download</a>\r\n\r\n<center>\r\n<h4 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Scientific Endorsements</strong></h4>\r\n</center>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<center><strong>Click on their logo to visit their website</strong></center><center>&nbsp;\r\n<table width="90%">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="CENTER" valign="TOP" width="50%"><a href="http://www.aimbe.org/" target="_blank"><img src="../../12adaimbe1.gif" alt="" width="278" height="85" border="" /></a></td>\r\n<td align="CENTER" valign="TOP" width="50%"><a href="http://www.bmes.org/" target="_blank"><img src="../../12adbmeslogo.gif" alt